headline: Franklin Resources, Inc. to Announce Fourth Quarter and Fiscal Year Results on November 7, 2025
summary: SAN MATEO, Calif., October 02, 2025--On Friday, November 7, 2025 at approximately 8:30 a.m. Eastern Time, Franklin Resources, Inc. (the "Company") [NYSE:BEN] will release its fourth quarter and fiscal year 2025 operating results. A written commentary on the results will also be available via investors.franklinresources.com at approximately 8:30 a.m. Eastern Time.
